About
Torrey Trails RV Resort offers guests to perfect sunny destination for the cold winter months or year-round enjoyment. When you stay at Torrey Trails, your job is to have fun - we’ll take care of the rest!
​
Torrey Trails is an RV Community founded by long-time developers who are synonymous with excellence - Bill Harvey, Amir Harpaz, and Jeff Cole.
​
As a locally-owned and operated RV resort, your experience is our primary goal.
Amir Harpaz
Jeffery Cole
Bill Harvey
